'''贝尔金·埃尔万'''（{{lang-tr|Berkin Elvan}}，{{bd|1999年|1月5日|2014年|3月11日|catIdx=Elvan}}）是一名15岁的[[土耳其人|土耳其]]男孩，2013年6月16日，他在2013年6月[[2013年土耳其反政府抗议运动|土耳其反政府抗议运动]]期间上街为家里买面包时，被一名警官的催泪瓦斯罐击中头部<ref name="theguardian">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/12/funeral-turkish-boy-berkin-elvan-thousands-istanbul-streets-protests-tear-gas-canister|title=Funeral of Turkish boy Berkin Elvan brings thousands to Istanbul streets | World news | theguardian.com|accessdate=2014-03-30|publisher=theguardian.com|archive-date=2014-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325063810/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/12/funeral-turkish-boy-berkin-elvan-thousands-istanbul-streets-protests-tear-gas-canister|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在昏迷269天后，于2014年3月11日去世。他家的代理律师说，埃尔文的健康状况在生命中的最后一周恶化，他的体重从45公斤下降到16公斤。<ref name="bbc">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26537211|title=BBC News - Grief breaks out as Turkish boy dies in coma|accessdate=2014-03-12|publisher=bbc.com|archive-date=2014-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312050301/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26537211|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="euronews">{{Cite web|url=http://www.euronews.com/2014/03/11/turkey-berkin-elvan-15-hurt-in-istanbul-clashes-dies-after-months-in-coma/|title=Turkey: Berkin Elvan, 15, hurt in Istanbul clashes, dies after months in coma | euronews,|accessdate=2014-03-12|publisher=euronews.com|archive-date=2014-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311225756/http://www.euronews.com/2014/03/11/turkey-berkin-elvan-15-hurt-in-istanbul-clashes-dies-after-months-in-coma/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hurriyetdailynews">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/15-year-old-gezi-victim-berkin-elvan-dies-after-269-days-in-coma-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=63429&NewsCatID=341|title=15-year-old Gezi victim Berkin Elvan dies after 269 days in coma  - LOCAL|accessdate=2014-03-12|publisher=hurriyetdailynews.com|archive-date=2014-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312020506/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/15-year-old-gezi-victim-berkin-elvan-dies-after-269-days-in-coma-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=63429&NewsCatID=341|dead-url=no}}</ref>贝尔金死亡后爆发了[[2013年土耳其反政府抗议运动|广泛的示威游行]]。<ref name="bbc2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26526198|title=BBC News - Turkey clashes after boy hurt at Istanbul protest dies|accessdate=2014-03-12|publisher=bbc.com|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024162014/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26526198|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/12/funeral-turkish-boy-berkin-elvan-thousands-istanbul-streets-protests-tear-gas-canister|title=Funeral of Turkish boy Berkin Elvan brings thousands to Istanbul streets|accessdate=12 March 2016|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723130653/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/12/funeral-turkish-boy-berkin-elvan-thousands-istanbul-streets-protests-tear-gas-canister|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他被埋在伊斯坦布尔Feriköy公墓。

